{"tid":1426068,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"警察通例","createTime":"2019-08-07T00:36:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T00:43:33.000Z","uid":293901,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a0af7bc8e3edb1374592edae0c5fafc315e36c04","tid":1426068,"uid":293901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:36:39.000Z","msg":"第二十章 第三節 20-03<br />\n<br />\n警署與各科組日常處理的事務<br />\n<br />\n在市民要求下披露身分<br />\n在不損害行動效率的情況下，人員於行使其法定權力時，在市民要求下應披露足以辨別其身分的個人資料。人員按要求表明身分後，應最低限度透露以下資料: <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">警員、警長、交通督導員及高級交通督導員: </span></strong>\t<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">職級及警務處職員編號</span></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">警署警長及以上職級 : \t<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">職級及姓氏</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n20-14 第二十章 十四節的第二點<br />\n<br />\n只要擬進行的工作不妨礙人員妥為保管委任證，警務人員在任何時候均須隨\t身攜帶委任證。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><ins>便衣人員不論是否當值，在與巿民接觸和行使警察權力時，必須表明身分及出示委任證。<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><ins><ins><span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\"><ins>在案發現場的便衣人員，</span></strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">須將委任證掛在顯眼的地方，讓人易於辨認其身分。</span></span></span></span></ins> </span></span></strong></span></ins></ins></span></ins><br />\n<br />\n20-14 第二十章 十四節 第四、第五點<br />\n<br />\n如市民提出要求，軍裝警務人員應出示委任證，除非： <br />\n(a)\t情況不容許；或 <br />\n(b)\t出示委任證會影響警隊行動及／或危及有關人員的安全；或 <br />\n(c)\t要求不合理。 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"color: green;\"><br />\n5.\t如軍裝警務人員在上文第4(a)及(b)段的情況下未能按要求出示委任證，其後待情況許可便應即時出示委任證。如警務人員沒有出示委任證，不論是要求不合理或最終未能遵辦，均須在記事冊內說明。</span></ins></strong></span>"},{"pid":"2024cd395c6c4329574f0f24c4482bd7a9549db2","tid":1426068,"uid":293901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:43:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/21950/%E7%9F%B3%E6%9B%B8%E9%8A%98-%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E7%B7%A8%E8%99%9F-%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E5%A7%94%E4%BB%BB%E8%AD%89-21953/%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E9%9B%86%E9%AB%94%E4%B8%8D%E5%87%BA%E7%A4%BA%E5%A7%94%E4%BB%BB%E8%AD%89%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E8%BF%BD%E7%A9%B6%EF%BC%9F-%E5%A4%A7%E7%8B%80%E7%9F%B3%E6%9B%B8%E9%8A%98%EF%BC%9A%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%E6%98%AF%E5%94%AF%E4%B8%80%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F21950%2F%25E7%259F%25B3%25E6%259B%25B8%25E9%258A%2598-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E7%25B7%25A8%25E8%2599%259F-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F%25E5%25A7%2594%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E8%25AD%2589-21953%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E9%259B%2586%25E9%25AB%2594%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2587%25BA%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A7%2594%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E8%25AD%2589%25E5%25A6%2582%25E4%25BD%2595%25E8%25BF%25BD%25E7%25A9%25B6%25EF%25BC%259F-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%258B%2580%25E7%259F%25B3%25E6%259B%25B8%25E9%258A%2598%25EF%25BC%259A%25E7%258D%25A8%25E7%25AB%258B%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5%25E6%2598%25AF%25E5%2594%25AF%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%25B3%2595&d=QE5rvD4iboeChbAAuj3apExj1a1M9JfR6d2dSWReNkw%3D&h=73bf35bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/21950/%E7%9F%B3%E6%9B%B8%E9%8A%98-%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E7%B7%A8%E8%99%9F-%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E5%A7%94%E4%BB%BB%E8%AD%89-21953/%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E9%9B%86%E9%AB%94%E4%B8%8D%E5%87%BA%E7%A4%BA%E5%A7%94%E4%BB%BB%E8%AD%89%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E8%BF%BD%E7%A9%B6%EF%BC%9F-%E5%A4%A7%E7%8B%80%E7%9F%B3%E6%9B%B8%E9%8A%98%EF%BC%9A%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%E6%98%AF%E5%94%AF%E4%B8%80%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95</a>"}]}